title: Great Stampede
author: Josophobia
pages:
#- There was once a man that told the rumors of a treasure. This is what he said:§0
§0Legend has it, that an old book can be found in the +,+ quadrant. Inside, there's a clue to a treasure map - one that leads to the treasure of Stampede The Great.
#- Legend also has it, there's an identical copy in the ruins of a great empire.§0
§0The books have a riddle which you must solve to get a clue to obtain the map.§0
§0However, it is a treacherous journey, for it is full of traps.§0
§0Good luck.
#- 